ai_summary.en: Amidst an 'Extreme Fear' macro environment, with the BTC Fear & Greed Index at 11, institutional whales on the ETH chain exhibit a largely neutral sentiment, marked by high volume but slight stablecoin outflows and no strong directional conviction. In stark contrast, the SOL chain sees a slightly bullish lean from retail/speculative players, evidenced by positive stablecoin inflows despite much lower overall volume. This divergence suggests institutions are exercising caution while retail attempts to find a bottom, hinting at potential short-term volatility and downside pressure until stronger institutional conviction emerges.
ai_summary.zh: 宏观市场弥漫着“极度恐惧”，比特币恐惧与贪婪指数仅为11。在此背景下，ETH链上的机构巨鲸情绪保持中立，交易量虽大但稳定币净流出微弱，未展现出强烈方向性。相比之下，SOL链上的散户/投机者则呈现出略微看涨的倾向，表现为稳定的净流入，尽管总交易量显著较低。这种分歧表明机构保持谨慎，而散户试图抄底，预示着短期市场可能持续波动，甚至进一步下行，直至机构出现更强的市场信心。
